---
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction">
  <div class="container-site hero__inner">
    <span class="hero__label animate-fade-up">
      Product design
      <span class="hero__sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      System design
      <span class="hero__sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      AI workflows
    </span>

    <h1 class="hero__headline animate-fade-up animate-delay-100">
      I build systems that<br />make complex things <em>usable</em>.
    </h1>

    <p class="hero__paragraph animate-fade-up animate-delay-200">
      I design and build product systems end to end. Most of the work lives
      inside long-running platforms where structure and consistency actually
      matter, and the design problem is usually the constraint, not the canvas.
    </p>

    <p class="hero__paragraph hero__paragraph--secondary animate-fade-up animate-delay-300">
      More recently, I've been building AI-native products and putting
      small agents into the workflows where they save real time.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-32));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-32);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: calc(64px + 176px);
      padding-bottom: 160px;
    }
  }

  .hero__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .hero__label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .hero__sep {
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 92px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    max-width: 15ch;
  }

  .hero__headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .hero__paragraph {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.5vw, 18px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    opacity: 0.92;
  }

  .hero__paragraph--secondary {
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
</style>
